email_chain.subject: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Hill,

Following your inquiry, please find our firm offer for the carriage of LNG, basis details as follows:

Commodity: LNG
Quantity: 8096 MT
Load Port: Suez Canal
Discharge Port: Algeciras
Incoterm: CIF
Vessel: OOCL TAIPEI (subject to chopt)

Freight: USD 44.98/MT, lump sum basis
Laycan: July 24-26, 2017

Please advise if this is of interest.

Best regards,
Raquel Patterson
Maritime Exchange Ltd.

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Patterson,

Thank you for the prompt quote. We appreciate the offer, however, $44.98/MT is above our target price. Given our longstanding relationship with Maritime Exchange and the volume of business we've placed with you over the years, could you please review the rate?

Ideally, we're looking for something closer to USD 42.00/MT. Please let me know if that's feasible. Also, could you confirm the vessel's DWT and LOA? 

Regards,
Kim Hill
Globex Shipping

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Hill,

Thank you for your email. I understand your position and appreciate your continued business.

I have reviewed the figures and can offer a revised rate of USD 43.75/MT. This is the best we can do at this time, given current market conditions in. 

To answer your question, the OOCL TAIPEI's DWT is 101,147 and LOA is 335 meters. 

Please advise if this revised offer is acceptable.

Best regards,
Raquel Patterson
Maritime Exchange Ltd.

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Patterson,

Thank you for the revised rate. We are still a bit apart. Could you meet us halfway at USD 43.00/MT? We need to confirm our stem by EOB tomorrow, so a quick response would be greatly appreciated.

Regards,
Kim Hill
Globex Shipping

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Hill,

Good Morning.

Understood. I have received authorization to fix at USD 43.00/MT. Please confirm your acceptance, and we will proceed with drafting the charter party agreement.

Thank you for your business.

Best regards,
Raquel Patterson
Maritime Exchange Ltd.

Disclaimer: This email is for informational purposes only and does not constitute a binding agreement until a formal charter party is executed.

email_chain.subject: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Hill,

Following your inquiry, please find our firm offer for the carriage of LNG, basis details as follows:

Commodity: LNG
Quantity: 8096 MT
Load Port: Suez Canal
Discharge Port: Algeciras
Incoterm: CIF
Vessel: OOCL TAIPEI (subject to chopt)

Freight: USD 44.98/MT, lump sum basis
Laycan: July 24-26, 2017

Please advise if this is of interest.

Best regards,
Raquel Patterson
Maritime Exchange Ltd.

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Patterson,

Thank you for the prompt quote. We appreciate the offer, however, $44.98/MT is above our target price. Given our longstanding relationship with Maritime Exchange and the volume of business we've placed with you over the years, could you please review the rate?

Ideally, we're looking for something closer to USD 42.00/MT. Please let me know if that's feasible. Also, could you confirm the vessel's DWT and LOA? 

Regards,
Kim Hill
Globex Shipping

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Hill,

Thank you for your email. I understand your position and appreciate your continued business.

I have reviewed the figures and can offer a revised rate of USD 43.75/MT. This is the best we can do at this time, given current market conditions in. 

To answer your question, the OOCL TAIPEI's DWT is 101,147 and LOA is 335 meters. 

Please advise if this revised offer is acceptable.

Best regards,
Raquel Patterson
Maritime Exchange Ltd.

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Patterson,

Thank you for the revised rate. We are still a bit apart. Could you meet us halfway at USD 43.00/MT? We need to confirm our stem by EOB tomorrow, so a quick response would be greatly appreciated.

Regards,
Kim Hill
Globex Shipping

email_chain.subject: Re: LNG Freight Quote - Suez/Algeciras
email_chain.body:
Dear Ms. Hill,

Good Morning.

Understood. I have received authorization to fix at USD 43.00/MT. Please confirm your acceptance, and we will proceed with drafting the charter party agreement.

Thank you for your business.

Best regards,
Raquel Patterson
Maritime Exchange Ltd.

Disclaimer: This email is for informational purposes only and does not constitute a binding agreement until a formal charter party is executed.

Thanks for the quick reply. $67.80 is a bit steep, even considering the urgency. Can you work on that rate at all? What's the vessel's loading window? What is the demurrage rate per day?

Thanks,
Evelyn

email_chain.subject: Re: Emergency Charter Request - Aluminum to Channel Islands
email_chain.body:
Evelyn,

I understand your concern regarding the rate. Considering the current market and the vessel's availability, I can revise it to $67.30/MT, FOB Ulsan to Channel Islands, still subject to stem. Loading window is tentatively March 5-7th. Demurrage rate is USD 25,000 per day or pro rata. Let me know if this is acceptable, sl!

Regards,
Kelsey

Roy Juarez
Seaway Commercial Brokers
